						               													<description>https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/cyborgcentaur/summoning&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The most powerful summoners are gathered to use their powers in an endless battle to prevail and survive.&amp;#10;Players are in control of characters, supporting creatures and&amp;#10;their abilities.&amp;#10;Each player is in control of a deck of cards with powers that are divided in 3 major aspects: Strength, Mind and Spirit.&amp;#10;Each aspect has it's own champions. For example, Strength has&amp;#10;Fighters and Rogues, while Mind has Wizards and Enchanters.&amp;#10;The game features 3 innovative mechanisms:&amp;#10;The first: Grey Magic. There is a category of magic that may be&amp;#10;used by the use of any power. Grey Magic can be harnessed by&amp;#10;either Strength, Mind or Spirit.&amp;#10;The second: Agendas. Agendas are powerful cards that change the&amp;#10;flow of the game, but, in order to enforce an Agenda, a player&amp;#10;must have influence in the Summoners Council.&amp;#10;The third: 3 gems of power help players acquire the proper kind&amp;#10;of power required to use their cards. These gems are divided in&amp;#10;the same aspects as their deck cards: Strength, Mind and Spirit.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game has many game modes:&amp;#10;2 players: 1 vs 1 or co-op&amp;#10;3 players: free-for-all or co-op&amp;#10;4 players: 2 vs 2, free-for-all or co-op&amp;#10;5 players: free-for-all, arena or co-op&amp;#10;6 players: 3 vs 3, 2 vs 2 vs 2 or co-op&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
